headline: U.S. Bank Avvance Launches Customized Embedded Financing Offering
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, October 21, 2025--Financial institutions and fintechs are now able to offer their customers simple, flexible embedded financing options that are tailored to their brand and experience thanks to the new U.S. Bank Avvance developer portal experience.
